    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document defines a YANG data model that can be used to configure and manage Network Time Protocol (NTP) version 4.  It can also be used to configure and manage version 3.  The data model includes configuration data and state data.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
